collectionMetadata.name: Bonus Quantum Paid
collectionMetadata.description: Data are collected from the Survey on Annual Wage Changes. The survey covers private sector establishments with at least 10 employees. The data collected pertain to full-time resident employees in continuous employment of at least one year.

datasetMetadata.name: Bonus Quantum Paid By Industry
datasetMetadata.description: Annual Variable Component usually consists of two components i.e. Annual Wage Supplement (also known as 13th month) and variable bonus.
